            <h3>💡 Remember:</h3>
             <ul>
                 <li><code class="ziggy-highlight-text">Podrías</code> is the conditional form of poder (could you).</li>
                 <li>Use <code class="ziggy-highlight-text">qué</code> for "what" and <code class="ziggy-highlight-text">por qué</code> for "why".</li>
                 <li><code class="ziggy-highlight-text">Cuánto</code> can be used for time (how long) or quantity (how much).</li>
                 <li>Pay attention to verb conjugations needed in questions!</li>
             </ul>
        </div>

